pan></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Basalt</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Deepslate</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Cobbled Deepslate</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Blackstone</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">End Stone</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Tuff</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Calcite</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Currently only available for the <strong>Fabric ModLoader</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Versions above <strong><code>0.1.1</code></strong> require <span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Chassis</strong></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MUtWKV8.png\" alt=\"\" /></span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/Libra\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://evergoodteam.github.io/img/sponsorBanner.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Want to play with some friends but setting up a server isn't easy? Just rent one already configured!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Click the image above (or click <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/Libra\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>), select a plan&nbsp;<br />and use the code&nbsp;<strong>Libra</strong>&nbsp;for <strong>25%</strong> off your first month with <strong>BisectHosting</strong>! </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Have fun!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zZ4rHFs.pn